headline: Design Software Stocks Q1 Teardown: Unity (NYSE:U) Vs The Rest
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q1. Today, we are looking at design software stocks, starting with Unity (NYSE:U).
